---
title: Spicy Cheesy Cauli-Stuffed Bell Peppers with Tex-Mex Spices, Zesty Rice & Lime Crema
description: Bold Southwest flavors abound in these roasted bell peppers stuffed with spiced rice and cauliflower. After filling the peppers, you’ll sprinkle them with a blend of Mexican-style cheeses and bake to melty, bubbly perfection. Zesty lime crema adds cool creaminess to the peppers, while lime-infused rice rounds out this flavorful meal.

